{"tid":2237317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"施政報告聯播論壇傳取消","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T07:12:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f121a1b04b4882c5a8d1fa7abd08246f3e49270","tid":2237317,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/4H7F3AALQVG45FL42DQPWILZFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2F4H7F3AALQVG45FL42DQPWILZFI%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDCMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=4c9463cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2F4H7F3AALQVG45FL42DQPWILZFI%2F&h=c50273e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/4H7F3AALQVG45FL42DQPWILZFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n施政報告聯播論壇傳取消<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥下周三發表新一份施政報告，有報道指，林鄭再度取消發表施政報告後出席電視台和電台的聯播論壇接受提問及聽取市民意見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年視像形式發表<br />\n<br />\n去年10月林鄭月娥到立法會宣讀施政報告時，正值反送中運動火熱之際。僅53段的施政報告未及宣讀完畢，林鄭就因為民主派抗議而放棄，改以視像形式發表，打破自1948年以來的傳統。<br />\n<br />\n去年林鄭發表施政報告前一星期，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n網媒《眾新聞》引述消息指，今年林鄭再度不出席電視台及電台聯播論壇，但未有提到原因。《蘋果》就相關問題向特首辦查詢，截稿前未有回應。以往行政長官發表施政報告當日及翌日，都會透過出席電視台及電台聯播論壇，接受記者提問和聽取市民意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sdpeLTkuD_2aDP7j_mBLp9FPq2E=/5184x3456/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DP5GYUGZ3JB2XMPWMILBL6UALQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsdpeLTkuD_2aDP7j_mBLp9FPq2E%3D%2F5184x3456%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDP5GYUGZ3JB2XMPWMILBL6UALQ.jpg&h=06da9622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2018年林鄭發表施政報告當日及翌日，有出席電視台及電台聯播論壇。資料圖片"},{"pid":"ec0a593d6d54d1a3604a5be5b5a7911a3945585b","tid":2237317,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"論咩壇姐, 其實真係唔洗做show wor.<br />\n立會一定通過, <br />\n下年仲有14億票比建制.<br />\n扮咩民主姐?"},{"pid":"e598169f279d779ecd6b1564084d5f62f576b14e","tid":2237317,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄邏輯：施政報告內容唔係政治問題，係一個事實既問題，如果倒轉黎講，如果係個論壇入面反對政府施政，大家係咪又可以接受？"},{"pid":"a2b3ebb1978317b8b45f171674c94f51af5b6a3a","tid":2237317,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"coward"},{"pid":"9290b71c7ed209e12ff6d157b9e6985af187bf0f","tid":2237317,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思幫我入嚟睇睇好嗎<br />\n[警世post] 終結失敗循環 面對獨裁絕不妥協<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}